Class GLAPPLEFence

java.lang.Object
overrungl.opengl.ext.apple.GLAPPLEFence
public final class GLAPPLEFence extends Object
GLAPPLEFence relies on preview features of the Java platform:
  • GLAPPLEFence refers to one or more preview APIs: MemorySegment, SegmentAllocator.
Programs can only use GLAPPLEFence when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
